What year is it?
Approx. MMM BC - creation of the first constellation maps.

What year is it?
MDXLIII - publication of Nicolaus Copernicus' work "On the Revolutions of the Heavenly Spheres".

What year is it?
MDCCLXXXIV - approximate determination of the shape and size of the Galaxy.

What year is it?

MCMLXI - first human flight into space.

What year is it?
MCMLXIX - first human landing on the Moon.

What year is it?
MCMXCVII - landing of a space probe on Mars and first exploration of the surface by a remotely controlled rover.

What year is it?
MMXXI - first drone flight on Mars.
